<br>
If the range of the spell is within the melee range of most mobs, swarm kiting is a non-issue. Even if people do manage to swarm successfully, the risk would be incredibly high. <br>
<br>
Charm hasn't been viable in groups since Luclin. From the time I got the first charm until PoP, charm was always in my 8th song slot. After PoP, I only mem'd it when I was farming or goofing around.<br>
