<br>
They also changed the str, atk, and damage shield max values for War March of the Mastruq and War March of Muram to make them scale with Jam Fest.  Luvwen's Lullaby (the lvl 67 OoW mez) now works to 70 instead of 68, so an appropriate increase there.<br>
<br>
Overall a good set of changes (IMO).  The max2 mana cap for Cantata/Chorus of Life still needs to be changed to 26 to allow for lvl 70 and JF, but that is the only JF related issue I can see at the moment.  The slow and HoS upgrade are still blank so we will have to see how they turn out.<br>
