<br>
Correct me if I am wrong but at the minute all the damage done to the charmed mob whilst charmed is 'unassigned' after charm breaks... why not change it so that the damage is left 'assigned' even after charm breaks so you could kill the mob but not recieve the exp as you did not actually do the damage necessary to recieve the exp... (I believe its currently 50% or so)<br>
<br>
This would immediatly cut out the benefit of swarm kiting and leave charm as a viable tool<br>
